title: BIP 5: Developer Mining Program Launch and Emissions
body:
Proposed by: Spadaboom

TLDR; Proposal to initiate Developer Mining Program

We propose 10,000 $BADGER tokens be allocated for developer rewards over the next 30 days. We are launching 2 new vaults on Sushiswap led by Andy8052

The 2 vaults are:
Badger/wbtc Sushi LP
wbtc/eth Sushi LP

With our first strategist we need to start emissions for the developer mining pool. As defined before launch, strategists earn 50% of the 20% performance fees from vaults they launch. They also earn emissions in $BADGER from the developer pool based on total TVL from their vaults.
